{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Sliding Image Showcase (3 per row)”
    
    Section Requirements
    
    Add up to 5 image blocks (each block for: image + title + subtitle + button link).
    
    Show blocks only if content is filled (if a block has no image, hide it automatically).
    
    Layout:
    
    Desktop → 3 items visible per slide
    
    Tablet → 2 items visible per slide
    
    Mobile → 1 item per slide
    
    Section must be a horizontal slider/carousel with:
    
    Left arrow
    
    Right arrow
    
    Pagination dots (optional toggle)
    
    Add editable border radius for each image block (global setting).
    
    Each image needs:
    
    1 editable image picker
    
    Title (optional, show/hide toggle)
    
    Subtitle (optional, show/hide toggle)
    
    Optional button text + link
    
    Arrow style:
    
    Round buttons
    
    User can change icon color and background color
    
    Slider should loop and support autoplay (toggle ON/OFF).
    
    Include spacing controls:
    
    Padding top/bottom
    
    Gap between items
    
    Code Output Requirement
    
    Output must be Shopify Liquid + JSON schema, ready for /sections/.
{% enddoc %}

